{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Where as we say in Rhodes Island, we didn't want to touch bologna-- not even knowing that it was human.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We thought it was from the cow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But then, you know, my father, want-- at the beginning-- 40 days, we will see the men, you know, from the other side of the fence.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were electric barbed, you know, wire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then my father-- that he was very well-- I mean, he knew very well, you know, the Hebrew, and all these laws, and all this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He told us in Hebrew, [HEBREW], which means the law of the government is the law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So if you don't eat, you'll starve, and you'll die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So God knows that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So don't-- don't-- forget about Kashrut and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Eat whatever they give you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the beginning, you know, we didn't want to-- even that we knew that, when we didn't want to touch that bologna.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after that, never mind, you know, we-- we ated anything they will give us-- especially when it come winter-- you know, it was very, very cold.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the whole-- and the whole, you know, horizon, we can see wherever you go, it was snow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not a single-- a single grass growing nowhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all snow-- snow, snow, snow everywhere-- all white.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was, you know, deep into the snow that we walked without shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many people, you know, while they were standing in the queue, I say, for three hours-- to be counted, they were frozen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they will not-- they will die there on the spot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes, you know, their feet, you know, they can get frozen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They cannot move anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they can-- they can be killed all the same.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
